FBIS4-3710 "drchi079_f_94011" FBIS-CHI-94-079 Daily Report 23 Apr 1994 Near East & South Asia Border Talks With China Focus on Force Reduction Border Talks With China Focus on Force Reduction BK2304091494 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0830 GMT 23 Apr 94 BK2304091494 Delhi All India Radio Network English BFN [Text] The two-day meeting of the Indo-China border expert group concluded in Beijing yesterday. It discussed among other things reduction of forces along the Line of Actual Control and other confidence building measures. The experts panel is part of the Indo-China Joint Working Group, JWG, which was set up in 1988. The JWG is scheduled to hold its next meeting in Beijing in the middle of the year.
